            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "School is good, but timings are tooooo long for kids ... Whole day kids are in school.. every day they have zero period, they do nothing for that period. this is just westing time. School starts at 8.20 am. A child has to leave for the school by 7.30 because most of the kids travel by bus, vans, rikshaw etc.. and school ends by 3.20 pm and child reach home by 4 pm. Have to give 2 tiffins breakfast and lunch with the child.. every day they eat cold tiffins.. Canteen facility is not proper.. they sale pav bhaji, Vada pav, noodles, kind of unhealthy food to kids .. kids don't get time for self study and other activities because they are already exhausted with long school hours.. It's affecting their mental and physical health and..it's really draining for kids..",
